content.raw:
Hi @{5d37c4ed2d50070c21a3c808}, thanks for the pull request. The model you're trying to upload doesn't look correct. The `model.sdf` file doesn't follow the spec and both files look like a copy from a file from someone else's  branch.

I'm declining this PR. Please check the tutorial on [How to contribute a model](http://gazebosim.org/tutorials?tut=model_contrib&cat=build_robot) for more detailed information on how to contribute models.
